<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Placement Gallery</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #f4f4f4;
    }

    h2 {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .gallery {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 25px;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .item {
      width: 320px;
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .item h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #333;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .item img, .item video {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .item p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #555;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <h2>Placement Gallery</h2>

  <div class="gallery">

    <div class="item">
      <h3>Campus Interviews</h3>
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1596079890749-460d6d1cfb34" alt="">
      <p>Top recruiters from various companies conducted on-campus interviews and selection rounds.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="item">
      <h3>Placement Orientation</h3>
      <video controls src="https://www.w3schools.com/html/movie.mp4"></video>
      <p>Students getting guided by placement officers about job interview preparation and resume building.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="item">
      <h3>Offer Letter Celebration</h3>
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551836022-d5d88e9218df" alt="">
      <p>Placed students sharing their success stories and receiving offer letters with joy and pride.</p>
    </div>

  </div>

</body>
</html>
